window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Juliette Salinger lives her life entirely on her mother’s terms. Everything from what she wears to who she dates is determined by what is deemed appropriate for their social standing. </p> <p>Look a little closer. </p> <p>Juliette isn’t cut out for that life. She lives for moments of reckless abandon to escape the crushing pressure of never being good enough. </p> <p>Leo Ashlar appears to live his life entirely on his own terms. He’s a bartending bachelor and undefeated fight-club champion. </p> <p>Look a little closer. </p> <p>He’s haunted by a tragic past and hides his demons even from those he loves. </p> <p>When Juliette’s worlds collide with the handsome and untouchable Leo, both are impacted in ways they couldn’t foresee. Juliette’s life begins to unravel. Can Leo help her build a new one, or will his past be their ultimate demise?</p>"; 
